When the animal gene activity was artificially reduced, they are less shouted at separation from the mother.
If the activity of a gene restored, reconstructed and the frequency of their calls.
Earlier on mice also shows the link with вокализацией the Foxp2.
Animals injected with human gene, squeaking faster and at a lower rate than normal mice.
